title: Green Mineral
description: A piece of green mineral with a rough texture, featuring various shades of green and some lighter inclusions.

title: Pyrite Cluster
description: A cluster of pyrite crystals, also known as 'fool's gold', showcasing its metallic luster and cubic crystal structure.

title: Abstract Shape
description: An abstract image featuring a white, cloud-like shape on a black background.

title: Mineral Sample
description: A cluster of dark, cubic mineral crystals with some lighter-colored facets. The crystals are irregularly shaped and vary in size, showcasing a mix of black and metallic hues.

title: Quartz Crystal Cluster
description: A cluster of clear quartz crystals, featuring several elongated points that extend outward from a central base. The crystals are transparent with a slight milky appearance, and some have a hint of yellowish mineral inclusions at the base.

title: Collection of Rocks and Minerals
description: A small collection of various rocks and minerals, including several larger pieces of gray and dark stones, along with a pile of white powdery substance and a smaller yellowish rock.
